QuestData.Title: Work Order: Kirin Tor Offensive II
QuestData.Description: Once your juicycrunch carrots are ready to be picked, you'll need only to package them for pick-up.$b$bJust think; your juicycrunch carrots will feed so many hungry soldiers on the front lines!
QuestData.LogDescription: Harvest 8 Ripe Juicycrunch Carrot plants and provide 40 Juicycrunch Carrots for the Kirin Tor Offensive.
